<qti-assessment-item xmlns="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0" xmlns:m="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" identifier="Q1_v6" title="Q1_v6" time-dependent="false" adaptive="false" xsi:schemaLocation="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0 https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/schema/xsd/imsqti_asiv3p0_v1p0.xsd">
  <qti-response-declaration identifier="RESPONSE" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier">
    <qti-correct-response>
      <qti-value>ChoiceB</qti-value>
    </qti-correct-response>
  </qti-response-declaration>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="FEEDBACK" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SOLUTION" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SCORE" cardinality="single" base-type="float">
    <qti-default-value>
      <qti-value>0</qti-value>
    </qti-default-value>
  </qti-outcome-declaration>
  <qti-item-body>
    <p>Considere la siguiente operación con números enteros:
      <m:math>
        <m:mrow>
          <m:mn>2</m:mn>
          <m:mo>-</m:mo>
          <m:mrow>
            <m:mo>(</m:mo>
            <m:mrow>
              <m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>3</m:mn>
            </m:mrow>
            <m:mo>)</m:mo>
          </m:mrow>
          <m:mrow>
            <m:mo>(</m:mo>
            <m:mrow>
              <m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>4</m:mn>
              <m:mo>-</m:mo>
              <m:mn>6</m:mn>
            </m:mrow>
            <m:mo>)</m:mo>
          </m:mrow>
        </m:mrow>
      </m:math>
    </p>
    <qti-choice-interaction response-identifier="RESPONSE" shuffle="false" max-choices="1">
      <qti-prompt>Cuatro estudiantes resolvieron esta operación y escribieron todo su procedimiento y resultado. ¿Cuál de los siguientes procedimientos es completamente correcto?</qti-prompt>
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceA">
        Estudiante 1: 2 − (−3)(−4 − 6) = 2 − (−3)(2) = 2 − (−6) = 8
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceA" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. En la expresión <m:math><m:mrow><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mrow><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>4</m:mn><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>6</m:mn></m:mrow><m:mo>)</m:mo><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mrow><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:mrow><m:mo>)</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math>, no <m:math><m:mrow><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mo>)</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math>. Luego, <m:math><m:mrow><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mrow><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:mrow><m:mo>)</m:mo><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mrow><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:mrow><m:mo>)</m:mo><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>30</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> y la operación completa es <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>30</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>28</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceB">
        Estudiante 2: 2 − (−3)(−4 − 6) = 2 − (−3)(−10) = 2 − 30 = −28
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceB" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">¡Correcto! Primero, <m:math><m:mrow><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>4</m:mn><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>6</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>. Después, <m:math><m:mrow><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mrow><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:mrow><m:mo>)</m:mo><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mrow><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:mrow><m:mo>)</m:mo><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>30</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>. Finalmente, <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>30</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>28</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceC">
        Estudiante 3: 2 − (−3)(−4 − 6) = 2 − (−3)(−10) = 2 − (−30) = 32
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceC" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Se tiene <m:math><m:mrow><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mrow><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:mrow><m:mo>)</m:mo><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mrow><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:mrow><m:mo>)</m:mo><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>30</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>, por lo tanto la expresión queda <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>30</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>, no <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mrow><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>30</m:mn></m:mrow><m:mo>)</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math>. Así, <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>30</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>28</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceD">
        Estudiante 4: 2 − (−3)(−4 − 6) = 2 − (−3)(−10) = 2 − 30 = 28
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceD" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Hasta <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>30</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> el procedimiento coincide con el cálculo correcto. Pero <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>30</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>28</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>, no <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>28</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
    </qti-choice-interaction>
    <qti-feedback-block identifier="show" outcome-identifier="SOLUTION" show-hide="show">
      <qti-content-body>
        <p><strong>Resolución paso a paso</strong></p>
        <ol>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 1: Resolver el paréntesis interior</strong></p>
            <p>Se calcula:
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>4</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>-</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>6</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                  <m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>10</m:mn>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>
            </p>
            <p>Entonces la expresión queda:
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mn>2</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>-</m:mo>
                  <m:mrow>
                    <m:mo>(</m:mo>
                    <m:mrow><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:mrow>
                    <m:mo>)</m:mo>
                  </m:mrow>
                  <m:mrow>
                    <m:mo>(</m:mo>
                    <m:mrow><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:mrow>
                    <m:mo>)</m:mo>
                  </m:mrow>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>
            </p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 2: Multiplicar los números enteros</strong></p>
            <p>Se multiplica:
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mrow>
                    <m:mo>(</m:mo>
                    <m:mrow><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:mrow>
                    <m:mo>)</m:mo>
                  </m:mrow>
                  <m:mrow>
                    <m:mo>(</m:mo>
                    <m:mrow><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:mrow>
                    <m:mo>)</m:mo>
                  </m:mrow>
                  <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>30</m:mn>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>
            </p>
            <p>Como el producto de dos números negativos es positivo, la expresión queda:
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mn>2</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>-</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>30</m:mn>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>
            </p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 3: Realizar la resta final</strong></p>
            <p>Se calcula:
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mn>2</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>-</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>30</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                  <m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>28</m:mn>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>
            </p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Conclusión</strong></p>
            <p>El procedimiento completamente correcto es el del <strong>Estudiante 2</strong>, correspondiente a la <strong>opción B</strong>.</p>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </qti-content-body>
    </qti-feedback-block>
  </qti-item-body>
  <qti-response-processing>
    <qti-response-condition>
      <qti-response-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SCORE">
          <qti-base-value base-type="float">1</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else>
    </qti-response-condition>
  </qti-response-processing>
</qti-assessment-item>